text: Love this special nostalgic feeling, so comforting, would like to visit this Aurora town if possible.
Favorite track: ダンサー

I’m in love with this! Listening to this gives me a super dreamy and warm feeing. The atmosphere is perfect. Listening to this, I’m getting heavy airport vibes. I get transported to an airport in a dream. The airport is covered in green and blue hues with a dreamy overlay that everyone seems to find normal besides me, I just want to explore this place instead of going to my flight. Amazing stuff!
Favorite track: コロンボ
this sounds so warm and cozy I FRICKIN love it
Favorite track: まだ午前中

Dear god, how do you do it. In this micro-world of sampled music having a a distinct and recognizable sound is twice as hard, yet you manage to have one. A great one. Each track is 100% Toyo and 100% good. It's the sound of a radio station that's playing somewhere, far from us, both in time and space. Once again, for the third time in a row, you delivered <3
Favorite track: ダンサー

description:
[CHILO-017]
それぞれのムードはスプリットアルバムです。それは2名のアーティストによって創作されました。
Each of mood is split album . It has been created by two artists .

豊平区民TOYOHIRAKUMIN https://toyohirakumin.bandcamp.com/
Eeyore https://eeyorefantasy.bandcamp.com/

スプリットアルバムを作成する主要な前提は、それがVaporwaveを動作させるとなり、 Vaporwaveもムード音楽として、お互いの気分は、それが仕事にということでした一枚であるの側面があることを2人での相互理解であるこのように住んでいる。この考え方に基づきアルバムのタイトルが（それぞれのムード=ムードのそれぞれ）となりました。
Became the major premise when creating a split album , it make the Vaporwave work , and Vaporwave is a mutual understanding of in two people that there is also the side of as mood music , mood of each other is one piece it was that to work , such as to live in . Album title Based on this concept became (Respective Mood = each of mood ) .
